{"article_id":"cUd9V7UFr1Es2fRY","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"J.K. Rowling spent Thursday","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"once again demonstrating a perplexing inability","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"to pipe down","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"and enjoy her millions .","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"This time , the Harry Potter author wasn ' t retconning diversity into the series","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"she finished writing over 12 years ago","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"or disclosing","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"that before indoor plumbing , the wizards of her universe used to just poop themselves","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"and magically vanish the evidence away .","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"Instead , Rowling tweeted her support for Maya Forstater , a tax expert","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"whose firing from a think tank over transphobic comments and subsequent court battle has generated a great deal of controversy in the U.K .","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"In so doing , Rowling seemed to align herself with a virulently anti-trans group of otherwise liberal women ,","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"most often referred to as trans exclusionary radical feminists or TERFs .","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"But force women out of their jobs","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"for stating","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"that sex is real ?","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"# IStandWithMaya","depth":6},{"id":17,"text":"# ThisIsNotADrill","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"- J.K. Rowling","depth":6},{"id":19,"text":"( @ jk_rowling )","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"December 19 , 2019","depth":5},{"id":21,"text":"\" Dress however you please , \"","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"Rowling wrote in a tweet .","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"\" Call yourself whatever you like .","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"Sleep with any consenting adult","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"who ' ll have you .","depth":11},{"id":26,"text":"Live your best life in peace and security .","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"But force women out of their jobs","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"for stating","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"that sex is real ?","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"# IStandWithMaya","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"# ThisIsNotADrill . \"","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"Rowling ' s tweet was immediately met with disappointment and anger ,","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"with critics pointing out","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"that she fundamentally misrepresented the Forstater case .","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"Forstater ' s contract with the Center for Global Development was not renewed due to a series of transphobic comments","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"made in multiple forums .","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"She repeatedly tweeted statements like ,","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"\" I think","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"that male people are not women .","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"I don ' t think","depth":12},{"id":41,"text":"being a woman/female is a matter of identity or womanly feelings .","depth":12},{"id":42,"text":"It is biology. \"","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"In a workplace Slack she wrote ,","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"\" But if people find the basic biological truths","depth":13},{"id":45,"text":"that ' women are adult human females '","depth":14},{"id":46,"text":"or ' transwomen are male '","depth":14},{"id":47,"text":"offensive ,","depth":12},{"id":48,"text":"then they will be offended. \"","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"Forstater also purposefully misgendered a nonbinary councilor on Twitter ,","depth":5},{"id":50,"text":"and","depth":7},{"id":51,"text":"when they complained ,","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"she wrote ,","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"\" I reserve the right","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"to use the pronouns ' he ' and ' him '","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"to refer to male people .","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"While I may choose to use alternative pronouns as a courtesy ,","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"no one has the right","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"to compel others to make statements","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"they do not believe . \"","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"In a suit","depth":7},{"id":61,"text":"filed against her former employer ,","depth":7},{"id":62,"text":"Forstater claimed","depth":6},{"id":63,"text":"that her contract nonrenewal was unjust","depth":6},{"id":64,"text":"and that her opinions should be protected ,","depth":7},{"id":65,"text":"as they were necessary for a \" free and open \" debate .","depth":7},{"id":66,"text":"The employment judge","depth":8},{"id":67,"text":"presiding over her case","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"didn ' t agree ,","depth":7},{"id":69,"text":"writing","depth":7},{"id":70,"text":"that Forstater ' s views did \" not have the protected characteristic of philosophical belief. \"","depth":7},{"id":71,"text":"In a 40-page decision","depth":8},{"id":72,"text":"released Wednesday night ,","depth":8},{"id":73,"text":"the judge stated","depth":7},{"id":74,"text":"that Forstater is \" absolutist in her view of sex","depth":7},{"id":75,"text":"and it is a core component of her belief that she will refer to a person by the sex","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"she considered appropriate","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"even if it violates their dignity","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"and/or creates an intimidating , hostile , degrading , humiliating or offensive environment .","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"The approach is not worthy of respect in a democratic society . \"","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"Rowling ' s support of Forstater and apparent endorsement of her anti-trans views isn ' t as surprising","depth":3},{"id":81,"text":"as it might seem at first glance .","depth":3},{"id":82,"text":"As Katelyn Burns noted in a March 2018 them . article ,","depth":4},{"id":83,"text":"Rowling has liked tweets","depth":6},{"id":84,"text":"that refer to trans women as \" men in dresses \"","depth":6},{"id":85,"text":"and arguably trafficked in anti-trans tropes in books","depth":6},{"id":86,"text":"she wrote under her pen name Robert Galbraith .","depth":6},{"id":87,"text":"Thursday ' s tweet was her most overt example of transphobia to date","depth":4},{"id":88,"text":"and demonstrates that ,","depth":5},{"id":89,"text":"despite previously positioning herself as an ally ,","depth":6},{"id":90,"text":"Rowling can not be considered a friend of the LGBTQ community .","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":181,"left":170,"right":180,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":170,"left":111,"right":169,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":111,"left":103,"right":110,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":103,"left":99,"right":102,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":99,"left":94,"right":98,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":94,"left":0,"right":93,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":93,"left":1,"right":92,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":92,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":98,"left":95,"right":97,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":95,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":97,"left":6,"right":96,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":96,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":102,"left":100,"right":101,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":100,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":101,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":110,"left":107,"right":109,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":107,"left":105,"right":106,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":105,"left":13,"right":104,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":104,"left":14,"right":15,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":106,"left":16,"right":17,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":109,"left":108,"right":20,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":108,"left":18,"right":19,"relation":"elaborati